data.description: Located on the highly desirable island of Ocean Ridge, you'll enjoy all the benefits of coastal living. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, this home is a blank canvas, ready for you to make it your own. This home is a rare opportunity to own so let your imagination run wild and create the beachside oasis you've always dreamed of. Ocean Ridge offers a tranquil and serene atmosphere, perfect for those seeking a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Indulge in the nearby dining and shopping options, or take advantage of the short stroll to the beach with its very own private beach access.
